summary:
Experienced Holistic Life Coach & Yoga Teacher working in the mental health, wellness and fitness industry. Skilled in event management, facilitating workshops & hosting retreats.

Acquired Yoga certification in RYT 200 hours yoga in 2016 Rishikesh , India continued Yoga certification in Yin Yoga & Yoga Therapy 

Educated in masters of Creative Arts Therapy & foundation in Chinese Medicine it my aim to enrich the lives of those she works with through cultivating body and mind awareness. Teaching diverse styles of Yoga/Pilates, Holistic wellness Workshops, Cacao ceremonies and therapeutic sessions to adults, adolescents and kids.
